[{"id":791557,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1626793722","description":"<p>在 iOS 上的「屏幕使用时间」中设置「抖音」每天只能刷 30 分钟，并且设置一个自己都不知道的密码！</p>\n<p>不知道是不是对自己狠了点</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gssgcbkq36j30u01sx0ty.jpg\"/></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/791557","replies":69,"created_ts":1627140418,"created":"23:26:58","title":"为了管住忍不住刷抖音的手，本程序员用了这个办法，非常有效，推荐大家试试","author":"shishirui","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/shishirui","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a774/3181/68275_mini.png?m=1405903206"},{"id":791522,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1615111825","description":"<p>楼主的需求主要是：\n1.上课看课件记笔记（ cs 专业）\n2.修图（ lightroom ）\n3.打游戏（吃鸡）</p>\n<p>目前二手 iPad Pro 2018 256G 在大概是 3800 上下，全新 iPad Pro 2021 128G 使用教育优惠后是 5799，再算上把耳机卖掉折算下来一个是 5100 上下。</p>\n<p>虽然中间的差价似乎只差了 1k，但我好像也用不到 M1 芯片的高性能，况且也担心 128G ROM 不够用。另一方面也不想花家里更多钱了，所以目前还是比较倾向买二手的 2018，但我还是希望能够请教一下各位的意见，小弟先在此谢过了。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/791522","replies":60,"created_ts":1627115773,"created":"16:36:13","title":"请教一下大家现在（2021.7.24）应该买 iPad Pro 2021 还是 2018 呢","author":"AlexMoriarty","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/AlexMoriarty","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4e499e579759caa219b5dc629446f174?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":791479,"node":"Windows","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1583044904","description":"<h2>前言</h2>\n<p>个人实测升级需要半个多小时，截至发帖时需要切换到 Dev 频道（即 Fast Ring ）获取更新。</p>\n<h2>展示图</h2>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://vip2.loli.io/2021/07/24/1ig3u7FqCRT9VJp.png\"/></p>\n<p>↑ 桌面及任务栏 （迫真 Macindows ）</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://vip2.loli.io/2021/07/24/rsnYAa4yKe97LiQ.png\"/></p>\n<p>↑ 文件资源管理器（左边可以直接看到 WSL 文件系统的入口了，不用再敲 <code>\\\\wsl$\\Ubuntu</code> 了）</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://vip1.loli.io/2021/07/24/6MLKYyUmS2oVrAN.png\"/></p>\n<p>↑ 系统版本</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://vip2.loli.io/2021/07/24/NY5TfiWsVvJC3Do.png\"/></p>\n<p>↑ 设置</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://vip2.loli.io/2021/07/24/Fg8LutnGIyY41OR.png\"/></p>\n<p>↑ 开始菜单</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://vip2.loli.io/2021/07/24/3rcRHelG7I9KWi5.png\"/></p>\n<p>↑ 任务管理器界面没有太大变化</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://vip2.loli.io/2021/07/24/UCrRmfD346nNzgc.png\"/></p>\n<p>↑ 右键菜单</p>\n<hr/>\n<p>其他的等以后有时间了再补充吧。</p>\n<h2>已知问题</h2>\n<p>这是我使用时遇到的一些问题 / 感觉不舒服的地方</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://aka.ms/AAda1wm\" rel=\"nofollow\">UAC 弹窗翻译错误</a></li>\n<li>窗口的圆角有锯齿</li>\n<li>微信 / QQ / TIM 等腾讯系软件最小化没有动画效果</li>\n<li>动态磁贴没了</li>\n<li>仍然没有旗帜类表情</li>\n</ul>\n<p>待补充...</p>\n<h2>后记</h2>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://vip2.loli.io/2021/07/24/sVHSC13iQE45TOy.png\"/></p>\n<p>（话说像我这种只体验不反馈的人是不是就算在浪费微软服务器带宽啊</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/791479","replies":46,"created_ts":1627095816,"created":"11:03:36","title":"没忍住，把主力机的系统升到了 Win 11（附图）","author":"baoshuo","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/baoshuo","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6bd5/cf64/486502_mini.png?m=1613975558"