ni.png?m=1588961795","description":"<ul>\n<li>华硕的 AC86U 路由器用了 4 年了，自从有了软路由，86U 就当做 ap 用了，这东西即便做 ap，从信号、延迟、网速等方面来说，体验比一般路由器也好挺多。</li>\n<li>夏天温度好像比较高，70 来度吧，也没在意，今天发现好像没反应了，重启重置啥的都不行。</li>\n<li>哎，提醒大家，设备也要做好防暑降温</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://img.mengma021.com/image-name/7RB0tcjV\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"7RB0tcjV.jpeg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://img.mengma021.com/img/2021-07-24/7RB0tcjV.jpeg\"/></a></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/791460","replies":36,"created_ts":1627088550,"created":"09:02:30","title":"AC86U 路由器，这是被热死了还是寿终正寝了","author":"maobukui","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/maobukui","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/dd5d4153dcfe4a6a47ea4a1907c8eb8f?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":791555,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1627019971","description":"<p>请问这是相当于降薪了吗？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/791555","replies":34,"created_ts":1627139118,"created":"23:05:18","title":"在武汉 18k， 上海 28k 的 offer 去不去？","author":"yycf","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/yycf","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8016d6fdf401ec58d654620af437e075?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":791536,"node":"macOS","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/macos","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1607656854","description":"<p>就 word/ppt，看电影。看啥特别需求。mac air 是合适的选择吗？还是有其他更好的推荐?</p>\n<p>air 怎么买划算? 只知道苹果官网。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/791536","replies":33,"created_ts":1627128989,"created":"20:16:29","title":"普通办公用电脑， mac air 够吗？","author":"exceldream","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/exceldream","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8e718b4ba1f98e68cd4cb55b4050446e?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":791462,"node":"iCloud","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/icloud","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f749/09ac/430_mini.png?m=1347578950","description":"<p>RT<br/>国区 2T 的 iCloud 空间满了，家里几个人自用的，有什么办法？求高手</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/791462","replies":31,"created_ts":1627089718,"created":"09:21:58","title":"2T 的 iCloud 家庭共享满了怎么办","author":"Brrrr","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Brrrr","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b826/3d4b/439703_mini.png?m=1588991731"},{"id":791454,"node":"宽带症候群","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1620107025","description":"每月 89 元，300M 宽带，三张卡共享 20G 和 300 分钟，IPTV 电视，送路由器和摄像头。<br />有点心动，我现在用的是 80 元 100M 宽带，三张卡共享无限流量和 700 分钟+IPTV 电视。<br />你们觉得应该更换这个新的套餐吗？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/791454","replies":29,"created_ts":1627083067,"created":"07:31:07","title":"广东电信良心发现，下乡扫村狂推 89 元 300M 宽带家庭套餐","author":"ChenCheChe","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ChenCheChe","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4995e65645e208f39441b8c9b5a48282?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":791443,"node":"生活","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/life","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","description":"<p>以下内容来自 MBA 智库百科：</p>\n<pre>缠论是网络名人“缠中说禅”关于证券市场的一种投资理论，缠论适合一切具有波动走势的投资市场，比如股票、权证和期货等，“缠师”2006 年 6 月 7 日写第一篇“教你炒股”系列文章开始，这个关于投资的理论“缠论”就正式面世。 ... 缠论是目前唯一能用数学手段进行证明的交易理论。\n</pre>\n<p>看了网上关于缠论的讨论非常多，很多人声称学了反而亏钱了，看起来缠论也比较难学。</p>\n<p>有没有大佬亲身经历实战证明。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/791443","replies":29,"created_ts":1627062997,"created":"01:56:37","title":"想学炒股，最近听说了《缠论》，有没有大佬使用该理论赚到钱的","author":"shenfu1991","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/shenfu1991","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/83687b54b474e861bc0c3853b099dd08?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":791510,"node":"生活","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/life","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","description":"我以前在前公司见过一种设备像个传统饮水机的，有热水、冷水的，也可以直出冰块的，也设备太大了，有没有小型的类似现在直饮机那种的。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/791510","replies":24,"created_ts":1627109430,"created":"14:50:30","title":"夏天了有没有设备可以 3 秒直能出冰块、冰水的直饮机？","author":"DreamCMS","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/DreamCMS","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5587/7f9a/104471_mini.png?m=1502675264"},{"id":791484,"node":"iOS","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/ios","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/069d/3bb0/580_mini.png?m=1611468295","description":"<p>不知道各位有没有经常使用 SiriKit，就是通过 Siri 直接给软件内的联系人发送信息，这个东西感觉还是挺方便的，比如不方便的时候需要发送信息直接嘿 Siri 就行了，QQ 从 6 点几版本开始适配 SiriKit，结果却从 8.0 开始停止适配😂，都已经做好了的功能都阉割掉。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/791484","replies":22,"created_ts":1627097671,"created":"11:34:31","title":"QQ8.0 开始不适配 SiriKit","author":"Suigintou","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Suigintou","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/19ed/bd4f/525038_mini.png?m=1613785274"},{"id":791450,"node":"NAS","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/nas","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3cef/96dc/949_mini.png?m=1614702882","description":"<p>宣传上每人 2T 去年还可以创建每个 250G 的群组空间<br/>\n2020 年 存了 38G 的文件进去 想着放一年再回来看看<br/>\n现在花了 5 小时 第一个 700M 文件重试了两次才下回来<br/>\n速度最高 100KB/s 最低 0.2KB/s 飘忽不定<br/>\n相比之下 年初也往阿里云放了一点文件 现在依然满速</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/791450","replies":22,"created_ts":1627076355,"created":"05:39:15","title":"大概两年前号称不限速的曲奇云盘(quqi.com)还是倒了 速度上成功升级为百度云级别","author":"Licsber","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Licsber","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5831/7907/241046_mini.png?m=1500390141"},{"id":791480,"node":"macOS","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/macos","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1607656854","description":"macOS 下按 Cmd+Tab 显示出来的是不同的软件切换。但如果一个软件有多个实例（比如开了两个 vscode 项目），多个实例又在多个桌面上（两个 vscode ）在不同桌面上，软件切换的方式就没法切换到目标窗口了。<br /><br />Windows 下的切换是以实例为粒度的，请问各位 macOS 下有类似的解决方案吗？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/791480","replies":21,"created_ts":1627096152,"created":"11:09:12","title":"macOS 下有什么快速切换窗口的方法吗？","author":"TripleZ","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/TripleZ","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8632a37f1bf7777a0658c8d8a0293b7e?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":791501,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1622572533","description":"<p>现在用的 AdGuard 作为家里神兽的网页浏览过滤方案</p>\n<p>使用的规则主要是域名和 URL 过滤，如下语法可以屏蔽搜索引擎的关键词“色情小说”</p>\n<pre><code>%E8%89%B2%E6%83%85%E5%B0%8F%E8%AF%B4$empty,domain=bing.com|baidu.com|google.com|so.com|sogou.com,important\n</code></pre>\n<p>但是如果 URL 中不含有这个词汇，就不能屏蔽了，比如通过网页上的链接打开。</p>\n<p>所以我希望能够从网页内容的 Title 里面搜索关键词，如果 Title 中有，就屏蔽整个页面的显示。</p>\n<p>研究它的规则一上午，没找到头绪，哪位大佬指点一下？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/791501","replies":17,"created_ts":1627106841,"created":"14:07:21","title":"AdGuard 的过滤规则请教","author":"ooyy","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ooyy","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ae73/c1ed/76340_mini.png?m=1614308646"},{"id":791533,"node":"分享创造","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/create","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1626270019","description":"<p>不知道大家有没有那样的经历，有时候在某度搜某些问题的时候总是找不到满意的结果，然后换某歌、某狗后一下子就找到了。感觉真是白白浪费时间。后来一想何不弄个聚合搜索入口，一键切换搜索引擎呢？\n于是利用业余时间做了下面这个东东，现在献给大家，希望大家喜欢。</p>\n<p>汤姆聚合搜索：<a href=\"https://www.tomfind.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.tomfind.com/</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>支持关键词联想  </li>\n<li>支持顶部栏、左侧栏两种界面模式</li>\n<li>包含谷歌代理搜索，无需 FQ</li>\n<li>纯静态程序，不使用 cookie，不记录用户任何搜索。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>界面截图：</h3>\n<p><img alt=\"搜索联想\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-270b4a87480f1fda7b8d848ce7767c1d_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></p>\n<h4>搜索联想</h4>\n<p><img alt=\"一键切换搜索引擎\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a5b4e0acae37439f7123ae1dc446c26e_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></p>\n<h4>一键切换搜索引擎</h4>\n<p><img alt=\"左侧栏模式\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-3a48de1b2940b5f1a6e0902bd12ceab6_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></p>\